channel.name: BBC One NL
channel.title: Strictly Come Dancing
channel.desc: Our couples are back on the dance floor for another weekend of ballroom dancing. Shirley Ballas, Craig Revel Horwood, Motsi Mabuse and Anton Du Beke will be keeping a close eye on proceedings, providing valuable insight and awarding scores, before the public vote opens at the end of the show. Who will take the top spot on the leaderboard this week?
